title: TEEN TOP's Niel shows off his boyish charm and masculine sexiness for 'GQ' | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me TEEN TOP's Niel shows off his boyish charm and masculine sexiness for 'GQ' By jennywill 53 minutes ago 3,187 684 0 1 Google+ TEEN TOP 's Niel managed to show off both his boyish charm and masculine sexiness in one photoshoot.
He had a photoshoot for the March issue of ' GQ ', and he went back and forth between the concepts and pulled them both amazingly. On his solo promotions, he said, " When I'm doing solo promotions, I really just do what I want. I think I'm still a rookie when it comes to solo promotions, and I don't get caught up in charts. I like hearing, 'Why is Niel doing that kind of song?' I want to try various genres. "
